{"tid":1055470,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"知識改變命運定係識人好過識字","createTime":"2019-03-10T14:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T01:53:56.000Z","uid":14378,"like":112,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3c7e00a7a8bf86e3d27dfc5ba4f99c33dd5595e4","tid":1055470,"uid":14378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:41:40.000Z","msg":"香港地<br />\n我覺得識人真係好識字<br />\n<br />\n無論你幾有學識幾有才華<br />\n無人賞識你 無人畀機會你發圍<br />\n你永遠都喺一嚿垃圾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識人好過識字<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知識改變命運"},{"pid":"a9820f05a928289e885a5b3945e28fe49bbcc63a","tid":1055470,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:42:20.000Z","msg":"必須正皮"},{"pid":"d104205573864399c18cc5ef06877b85a7e48b69","tid":1055470,"uid":192491,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:44:03.000Z","msg":"why not both"},{"pid":"3bd62d8f3aea74f2d9916f365507bbf3b6350ba1","tid":1055470,"uid":41355,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:45:01.000Z","msg":"錯，係成功需父幹"},{"pid":"285cf33e5de69ab5e0534e5970408f46d79585df","tid":1055470,"uid":192571,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:49:21.000Z","msg":"係一出世就注定識到邊啲人"},{"pid":"27dcfa311bbc2c1e6219522a01bbc332278f1b36","tid":1055470,"uid":14378,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3bd62d8f3aea74f2d9916f365507bbf3b6350ba1","tid":1055470,"uid":41355,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:45:01.000Z","msg":"錯，係成功需父幹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:16:49.000Z","msg":"撇除成功需父幹呢個天生條件<br />\n<br />\n當你係一個草根家庭出世<br />\n無論你幾有學問<br />\n無人識你就喺無人識你<br />\n你永遠都係一個平凡嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/70b/1a9/70b1a988524d8b59fc417b566b885f300b8fc88c_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F70b%2F1a9%2F70b1a988524d